    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable per the MRL 2 assessment plan. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification across all model inputs confirms that the hemolysis index prediction is robust to input variability, with the 95th percentile RH remaining below 1.0 across the COU operating envelope. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
